data.description: Welcome Home to this charming 3 bedroom 2 bath CBS home in Port St Lucie.  This home has a BRAND NEW ROOF and the solar panels will be paid off by the sellers at closing.   New wood plank tile in the Owners Suite and a remodeled Primary Bathroom.   Two guest rooms with large walk in closets and guest bath doubles as cabana bath! There is a large screened in porch with pass through window making it a great entertaining space.  Large backyard which is fully fenced! New Tankless Water Heater   New AC   New Kitchen Appliances   New Washer & Dryer   If you are ready to move to Florida, here is your opportunity to have a beautiful home at a great price!
